<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
   
</head>
<body>
    <section id="nosotros" class="seccion-nosotros">
        <div class="contenedor-nosotros">
          <div class="texto-nosotros">
            <h2>Who we are</h2>
            <p>
              In <strong>Restorer's Corner</strong>,we believe that baking is an art form. Every cake, every cookie, every creation is born from the precise blend of technique, passion and respect for the ingredients.
              <br><br>
              Since our inception, we set out to go beyond taste: we seek to provoke emotions, memories and experiences in every bite. With a careful aesthetic, traditional recipes and a contemporary touch, we offer more than just sweets - we offer character.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="imagen-nosotros">
            <img src="somos.jpg" alt="Repostero trabajando">
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>
      
      <style>
        .seccion-nosotros {
          padding: 100px 20px;
          background: linear-gradient(to right, #f3e9e4, #f8f5f2);
          color: #2d2d2d;
        }
      
        .contenedor-nosotros {
          max-width: 1100px;
          margin: 0 auto;
          display: flex;
          align-items: center;
          gap: 60px;
          flex-wrap: wrap;
        }
      
        .texto-nosotros {
          flex: 1 1 500px;
        }
      
        .texto-nosotros h2 {
          font-size: 2.8rem;
          margin-bottom: 20px;
          font-weight: 600;
          color: #3c2f2f;
          border-left: 5px solid #361b02;
          padding-left: 15px;
        }
      
        .texto-nosotros p {
          font-size: 1.2rem;
          line-height: 1.8;
          color: #4b4b4b;
        }
      
        .imagen-nosotros {
          flex: 1 1 400px;
          text-align: center;
        }
      
        .imagen-nosotros img {
          width: 100%;
          max-width: 450px;
          border-radius: 15px;
          box-shadow: 0 10px 25px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
          object-fit: cover;
        }
      
        @media (max-width: 900px) {
          .contenedor-nosotros {
            flex-direction: column-reverse;
            text-align: center;
          }
      
          .texto-nosotros h2 {
            border-left: none;
            padding-left: 0;
            border-bottom: 3px solid #361b02;
            display: inline-block;
            margin: 0 auto 20px auto;
          }
        }
      </style>
    
</body>
</html>